Task 1: Credit Risk Analysis (Data Cleaning)
Objective: Prepare a raw financial dataset for machine learning by handling missing values and outliers.

Key Skills: Data Imputation, Schema Alignment, Outlier Detection.


Technical Challenges Overcome: Resolved KeyError and AttributeError by identifying that the dataset used non-standard column names like Bank Balance and Annual Salary instead of expected defaults.

Outcome: A cleaned, normalized dataset ready for predictive modeling.
